{"title":"Book of Minor Magic","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Book_of_Minor_Magic","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.26](/0.26 \"0.26\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n| [![Spellbook.png](/images/0/0d/Spellbook.png)](/File:Spellbook.png) Book of Minor Magic |   |\n| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | - |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                       |\n| - | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | A spellbook containing a variety of simple but useful magical incantations. Many prominent spellcasters used this book to begin their arcane studies. |\n\nThe **Book of Minor Magic** is the starting book of the [Hedge Wizard](/Hedge_Wizard \"Hedge Wizard\") background.\n\n## Spells\n\n| Tile                                                                   | Spell                                      | Type                                              | Level |\n| ---------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------- | ----- |\n| [![Magic dart.png](/images/4/47/Magic_dart.png)](/File:Magic_dart.png) | a - [Magic Dart](/Magic_Dart \"Magic Dart\") | [Conjuration](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")       | 1     |\n| [![Blink.png](/images/1/16/Blink.png)](/File:Blink.png)                | b - [Blink](/Blink \"Blink\")                | [Translocation](/Translocations \"Translocations\") | 2     |\n| [![Call imp.png](/images/4/47/Call_imp.png)](/File:Call_imp.png)       | c - [Call Imp](/Call_Imp \"Call Imp\")       | [Summoning](/Summonings \"Summonings\")             | 2     |\n\n## Strategy\n\nThis is a great starting book for beginners, as Mephitic Cloud and Call Iimp can easily get you through the early game. Blink can get you out of nasty situations pretty quickly, and Conjure Flame can help keep most enemies at bay. However, once you encounter the Lair, the spells this book provides aren't strong enough anymore and you'll need help of other spells or items to survive there.\n\n## History\n\n- In [0.20](/0.20 \"0.20\"), [Repel Missiles](/Repel_Missiles \"Repel Missiles\") was removed.\n- It was added in [0.8](/0.8 \"0.8\") as a replacement for three different Wizard starting books: [flame](/Book_of_Minor_Magic_\\(flame\\) \"Book of Minor Magic (flame)\"), [frost](/Book_of_Minor_Magic_\\(frost\\) \"Book of Minor Magic (frost)\"), and [summoning](/Book_of_Minor_Magic_\\(summ\\) \"Book of Minor Magic (summ)\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Book of Minor Magic - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Book_of_Minor_Magic\",\"wgTitle\":\"Book of Minor Magic\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":54454,\"wgRevisionId\":54454,\"wgArticleId\":2009,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.26 articles\",\"Book\",\"Starting Books\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort