\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> <a href=\"/File:Spellbook.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spellbook.png\" src=\"/images/0/0d/Spellbook.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#8195;Book of Minor Magic\n</th></tr>\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A spellbook containing a variety of simple but useful magical incantations. Many prominent spellcasters used this book to begin their arcane studies.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>The <b>Book of Minor Magic</b> is the starting book of the <a href=\"/Hedge_Wizard\" title=\"Hedge Wizard\">Hedge Wizard</a> background.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Spells\">Spells</span></h2>\n<table cellpadding=\"5\" border=\"1\">\n\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<th> Tile </th>\n<th> Spell </th>\n<th> Type </th>\n<th> Level\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Magic_dart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Magic dart.png\" src=\"/images/4/47/Magic_dart.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> </td>\n<td> a - <a href=\"/Magic_Dart\" title=\"Magic Dart\">Magic Dart</a> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/Conjurations\" title=\"Conjurations\">Conjuration</a> </td>\n<td> 1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Blink.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Blink.png\" src=\"/images/1/16/Blink.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> </td>\n<td> b - <a href=\"/Blink\" title=\"Blink\">Blink</a> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/Translocations\" title=\"Translocations\">Translocation</a> </td>\n<td> 2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Call_imp.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Call imp.png\" src=\"/images/4/47/Call_imp.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> </td>\n<td> c - <a href=\"/Call_Imp\" title=\"Call Imp\">Call Imp</a> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/Summonings\" title=\"Summonings\">Summoning</a> </td>\n<td> 2\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>This is a great starting book for beginners, as Mephitic Cloud and Call Iimp can easily get you through the early game. Blink can get you out of nasty situations pretty quickly, and Conjure Flame can help keep most enemies at bay. However, once you encounter the Lair, the spells this book provides aren't strong enough anymore and you'll need help of other spells or items to survive there.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.20\" title=\"0.20\">0.20</a>, <a href=\"/Repel_Missiles\" title=\"Repel Missiles\">Repel Missiles</a> was removed.</li>\n<li>It was added in <a href=\"/0.8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"0.8\">0.8</a> as a replacement for three different Wizard starting books: <a href=\"/Book_of_Minor_Magic_(flame)\" title=\"Book of Minor Magic (flame)\">flame</a>, <a href=\"/Book_of_Minor_Magic_(frost)\" title=\"Book of Minor Magic (frost)\">frost</a>, and <a href=\"/Book_of_Minor_Magic_(summ)\" title=\"Book of Minor Magic (summ)\">summoning</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916113422\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU tim